title: Trynda and nasus same team
body: So i just played game where enemy had nasus top and trynda jungle. Endless splitpush every lane, teamfights impossible to kill all. How can u deal with that? It just seemed there is no way on earth to stop them

replies.body:
Group as 5 mid and push for inhab/nexus...

If your team couldn't win a 3 v 5 thats just on your guys.

> [{quoted}](name=Santeri20,realm=EUNE,application-id=3ErqAdtq,discussion-id=AwUwsovB,comment-id=,timestamp=2017-05-29T19:32:54.211+0000)
>
>Endless splitpush every lane, teamfights impossible to kill all. 

So you couldn't win a 5v3. In what way did it matter that Trynd and Nasus were on the team?
If anything that should have been an easy game. If they are double splitpushing then you should have had won easily the 5 v 3s plus objectives.
Take advantage when you have a numbers advantage
You don't. You 5 man the nexus.
